        "TileImage": "$($repository 53406e7a-83d4-4dfd-a5f9-839d6f5e3baa).Image",
        "Description": "Internal sleuthing has revealed a dire story: Mr. Hopperson has been lying this whole time. None of the victims were guilty of the sins he painted them with. Now your decision comes to bear, either finish your initiation, and slaughter the plumber with the ritual dagger that came with the instructions, or murder the overseer Mr. Hopperfield has assigned to watch the nieghborhood. Through clever detective work, you have learned his cover identity and can take him out. The choice is yours.",
